Always Apply: true
Margin: 32px
Gutter: 15px
Columns: 12
Within Container Margin: 24px
Background: #FFFFFF
Theme Color: #D32F2F (Red)
Accent Color: #E53935
Text Color: #000000
Secondary Text: #444444
Font Family: "Inter", "Poppins", "Roboto", sans-serif
Base Radius: 12px
Base Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)

Heading 1 (H1):
  - Desktop: 28px / 700
  - Tablet: 24px / 700
  - Mobile: 20px / 600

Heading 2 (H2):
  - Desktop: 22px / 600
  - Tablet: 20px / 600
  - Mobile: 18px / 600

Body Text:
  - Desktop: 16px / 500
  - Tablet: 15px / 500
  - Mobile: 14px / 500

Main Content Font Size:
  - All main frame content: 14px
  - Icons scaled proportionally smaller to match content
  - Maintain readability and visual hierarchy

Mobile Font Size Scaling:
  - Desktop: 100% (base sizes)
  - Tablet (≤768px): 90% of desktop sizes
  - Mobile (≤480px): 80% of desktop sizes
  - Ensure all text remains readable and forms fit properly
  - Apply to all typography: headings, body text, form labels, buttons

Small Text:
  - Desktop: 13px / 400
  - Tablet: 12px / 400
  - Mobile: 12px / 400

Font Color: #000000
Line Height: 1.5
Letter Spacing: 0.2px

Container Widths:
  - Desktop: 1200px max
  - Tablet: 90%
  - Mobile: 100%

Page Padding:
  - Desktop: 24px
  - Tablet: 16px
  - Mobile: 12px


Container Background: #FFFFFF

Position: fixed
Location: left
Width:
  - Expanded: 240px
  - Collapsed: 80px
Height: 100vh
Background: #FFFFFF
Border-Right: 1px solid #E0E0E0
Box-Shadow: 2px 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)
Padding: 16px 0
Z-Index: 999
Transition: width 0.3s ease

Menu Items:
  - Display: flex (icon + label)
  - Padding: 12px 20px
  - Border-Radius: 10px
  - Font Size: 15px
  - Font Weight: 500
  - Color: #444444
  - Icon Size: 20px
  - Hover: background #FDEAEA, text #D32F2F
  - Active: background #D32F2F, text #FFFFFF
  - Icon Active Color: #FFFFFF

Collapsible Behavior:
  - Collapse button on bottom or top-right
  - On collapse: hide labels, show icons only
  - Tooltip: show label on hover
  - Mobile: sidebar slides out as overlay

Responsive Behavior:
  - Desktop: fixed expanded
  - Tablet: collapsible
  - Mobile: hidden (toggle via menu button)

Position: fixed (top)
Z-Index: 1000
Height:
  - Desktop: 72px
  - Tablet: 64px
  - Mobile: 56px
Width: 100%
Background: #FFFFFF
Border-Bottom: 1px solid #E0E0E0
Box-Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)
Padding:
  - Desktop: 0 24px
  - Mobile: 0 16px
Display: flex
Align-Items: center
Justify-Content: space-between

Left Section — Active Page Title:
  - Font Size: Desktop 20px / Tablet 18px / Mobile 16px
  - Font Weight: 600
  - Color: #000000
  - Text Transform: capitalize
  - Responsive: truncate long titles

Center Section — Search Bar:
  - Width: Desktop 420px / Tablet 320px / Mobile hidden
  - Height: 40px
  - Background: #F5F5F5
  - Border: 1px solid #E0E0E0
  - Border-Radius: 12px
  - Padding: 0 14px
  - Icon: search (left side, #777)
  - Placeholder: "Search..." (14px, #666)
  - Focus: border #D32F2F, bg #FFFFFF, shadow 0 0 4px rgba(211,47,47,0.2)
  - Mobile: replaced with search icon that opens overlay search modal

Right Section — Notification & Profile:
  Notification Icon:
    - Size: 24px
    - Color: #444444
    - Hover: #D32F2F
    - Badge: small red dot (8px, #D32F2F)
    - Dropdown:
        Width: 320px
        Background: #FFFFFF
        Border-Radius: 12px
        Border: 1px solid #E0E0E0
        Box-Shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)

  User Profile:
    - Avatar: 36px circle
    - Hover: soft red outline (#FDDDE0) or subtle scale
    - Dropdown: “Profile”, “Settings”, “Logout”
    - Mobile: 32px avatar, dropdown uses bottom-sheet style

Responsive Behavior:
  - Desktop: title + search + notifications + profile
  - Tablet: smaller search, same layout
  - Mobile: title left, search hidden (icon only), notifications + profile visible

Actions (Global Rule):
  - All actions in any form or page should be icon-only controls
  - Provide clear aria-label and title attributes for accessibility
  - Use consistent iconography from the approved set (Lucide, Material Symbols)
  - Optional tooltips may be shown on hover/focus
  - When necessary, show text labels on very small screens only

Dialogs (Alerts/Confirms/Prompts):
  - Must use app-themed modal components, not browser-native dialogs
  - Backdrop: semi-transparent black (40%), blur optional; closes on explicit action only
  - Container: white background, base radius 12–14px, subtle shadow
  - Header: title 18–20px / 600
  - Body: 14–16px secondary text color
  - Actions: right-aligned icon-first buttons; primary uses Theme Color, danger uses Accent/Error
  - Actions Area: clean white background, NO colored fill or background color
  - Dialog bottom section (where controls/buttons are) must have transparent or white background only
  - Accessibility: focus trap, ESC to cancel, aria-modal, role=dialog, labels/ids wired
  - Responsive: max-width ~560–640px, 92vw on mobile
